        <abstract>
            <p>Plans visit to Ceylon.</p>
            <p>Describes rejection of his application for funds by Berlin Academy. Asks about possibility of obtaining support in England. Is writing to Lubbock and Huxley about it.</p>
            <p>Hopes that new microscope from Zeiss is satisfactory. Ernst Abbe selected lenses.</p>
        </abstract>
